{"word":"γόνυ","slug":"γόνυ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γόνυ, ατος, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> genu] <b><i>knee</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as body part <b><a href='B:650 12:12'>Hb 12:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> such verbs as <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κάμπτω\">κάμπτω</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:προσπίπτω\">προσπίπτω</a>, τίϑημι</el> in gesturing position of getting down on one’s knee(s): for petition or prayer <b><a href='B:490 5:8'>Lk 5:8</a>; <a href='B:490 22:41'>22:41</a>; <a href='B:510 7:60'>Ac 7:60</a>; <a href='B:510 9:40'>9:40</a>; <a href='B:510 20:36'>20:36</a>; <a href='B:510 21:5'>21:5</a>; <a href='B:560 3:14'>Eph 3:14</a>;</b> in adulation <b><a href='B:480 15:19'>Mk 15:19</a>; <a href='B:520 11:4'>Ro 11:4</a>; <a href='B:520 14:11'>14:11</a>; <a href='B:570 2:10'>Phil 2:10</a>.</b> For the formula <el>τιϑέναι γόνατα</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> ponere genua <i>get down on one’s knees</i> = <i>bow the knee.</i> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γονεύς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:γονυπετέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}